  enabled: true
  base_url: "https://n8n.ddtool.tech"
mcp_cron:
  enabled: false
---

# DefTrello Board Configuration

This file stores your board preferences and is never committed to git.

## Setup Instructions

1. Copy this file to `.claude/deftrello.local.md` (remove .example)
2. Update `current_board_id` and `default_board_id` with your Trello board ID
3. Add your boards to the `boards` array
4. Get board ID from Trello board URL: trello.com/b/YOUR_BOARD_ID/board-name
5. Get list IDs using: `/deftrello:board-list` command

## Fields

- **current_board_id**: The board currently being used for operations
- **default_board_id**: Fallback board when no board specified
- **boards**: Registry of known boards with list ID mappings
- **wip_limits**: Work-in-progress limits (customize per your workflow)
- **n8n**: n8n integration settings
- **mcp_cron**: Enable MCP-CRON integration for scheduled tasks

## Usage

Commands will automatically use `current_board_id` unless you specify a different board.

Switch boards with: `/deftrello:board-select`
List all boards with: `/deftrello:board-list`
